  "instructions": "<p>Good place for experience and money for knights level 35 to 60. Recommended skills is 65/65+.</p>\n<p>It's less contested than Darashia Dragon Lair, so it can be a good alternative spot. Very close to Venore, what makes it easy to resupply and make lootbags.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üõ°Ô∏è<strong> Equipments</strong></p>\n<p>A Knight Set or Crown Set is all you gonna need. But it is very important to carry an Obsidian Knife. Using it to skin dragons for leathers will add a nice profit to your hunts.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Killing dragons doesn't require imbuements, but if you are willing to, mana and crit are good options.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üíØ <strong>Experience</strong></p>\n<p>It's possible to make between 100k to 130k of experience per hour and up to 200k/h on green stamina.&nbsp;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üí∞ <strong>Profit</strong></p>\n<p>Usually there will be no profit nor waste here.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>‚öîÔ∏è<strong> Strategy</strong></p>\n<p>To increase the hunt time and have less waste use spells only when there are more than 2 dragons. When there is only one, just do melee attacks.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>However, if you want to push the experience just keep using <em>exori ico</em> and <em>exori hur</em> every time it is available, but you should save the <em>exori</em> for when there's 2 or more dragons.</p>",
